papilog 0.1

Usage: papilog -pINT|--pid=INT [-h|--help] [-V|--version] [-v|--verbose]
         [-eSTRING|--event=STRING] [-iINT|--interval=INT] [-r|--reset]
         [-t|--timestamp]

PAPI-based performance counter logger.

  -h, --help          Print help and exit
  -V, --version       Print version and exit
  -v, --verbose       Verbosity. Repeat for more verbose.
  -p, --pid=INT       PID of process to monitor. (mandatory)
  -e, --event=STRING  PAPI event to monitor.  May be repeated.
  -i, --interval=INT  Interval for counter reporting.  (default=`5')
  -r, --reset         Reset counters after each report.
  -t, --timestamp     Timestamp reports.
